verbose_text: After conditioning on the four FLG null mutations and the LCE3B-LCE3C deletion, the G allele of the lead MNM SNV rs12130219 decreases the risk for AD (OR ADcond = 0.812, p ADcond = 0.0018) and increases the risk for psoriasis (OR PSOcond = 1.119, p PSOcond = 3.68 x 10 -4) (XREF_TABLE).
evidence: G allele of the lead MNM SNV rs12130219 decreases the risk for AD
